tws.ADMBlending.InfoText: Accelerated Dialing Model feature helps to allocate the agents between Consent and Non-Consent dialer. Non-Consent dialer usually dials only Non-consent numbers and those will be delivered to Control agent. When Control Agent initiating the contact, it will be dialled to the customer and connect with agent. It is not advised to enable PEWC feature at the campaign while Accelerated Dialing Model feature is set to off.
tws.AgentAlignmentHelp: Agent Alignment (Default) field helps to assign the agents to the default dialer when all blending group minimum requirements are filled.
tws.NTPCBTimeoutHelp: The number of seconds to which, Callback Task can stay in the Queue. Post which, the Callback Task will be timedout. Allowed Values : Between 1 and 36000 seconds, Default Value : 1800 seconds
